review: The game is not the type of game i like nor dislike but i think that people should buy it if they like a challenge to make sure you can enjoy the game play the campaign it is extremely fun but on the last part in the rulers mind i could not find anything and nothing happened so sadly my game might have bugged and not loaded anything
developer_response:
Oh no!

Was it towards the section guarding the Core Instruction behind a red laser wall? To get past it you have to kill yourself on the saw blades in front of it to trigger a mind transfer into one of the guards behind it.

Or if it was a bug, exiting the game and starting up story mode again should fix it. Sorry you got stuck regardless! There's a pretty cool fight on the other end of it if you do try it again. :)

Cheers,
Erik

review: 从大概2016年这个游戏出来，我就从屌德斯的视频上看，特别喜欢这个游戏，还有分析机器人和评论机器人，他们从游戏刚出就一直陪伴着玩家，虽然他们经常想看玩家死，但是好歹也是一直陪着玩家的，2018年我从快吧游戏盒上玩这个游戏，当时版本老，只是踢挑战刚出的时候，很想玩他们的版本但又没钱买正版，直到去年再次登录发现了更新到了第四章很开心，不知何时更到了第五章，但是想玩多人但没钱买就去借了点钱，买了，如果评论机器人和分析机器人被删除或者改样子，我将去下一个老版本的，再也不碰新版

author: {'steamid': '76561199219255902', 'num_games_owned': 114, 'num_reviews': 42, 'playtime_forever': 2409, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 591, 'last_played': 1707851791}
review: in clone drone, your a clone. i know big shocker i was too i had to take a 30 minute breaking from this game since i pissed myself after finding out. now back to the game. you play as whoever you got from the machine, and you gotta slice and dice dudes, or smash and bash or use like a spear and go shinggg, or even a bow and go fligngnhgng. then after you finish doing that you upgrade yourself and then the dudes you were fighting get replaced by stronger dudes and cooler maps. thats the entire game. its a physics based fighting system and its a bit janky but fun. there is some stages where you are just running away from the enemys, then go in and go back to running away from enemies. the humour in this game is good but after playing it for 5 hours+ the same lines repeat. this game is really good, its got a co-op aswell, never played it since i dont got friends and it got a fortnite mode, where you play fortnite, and everyone else uses op loadouts and kills you instantly. that mode is my favourite. i would give this game a 9/10. you get what your paying for, even better if its on sale.

author: {'steamid': '76561198095508583', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 28, 'playtime_forever': 615, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 615, 'last_played': 1661538960}
review: I am a 45 yo father, probably one of the oldest people playing this game. I am a single farther to my Son, who is 14 now. My son got this game for Christmas in 2021 from his uncle, so we installed it on his computer and he started playing. By the end of the week he had 24 hours on this game. This was horrible for me, as it was already hard for me to find ways to spend time with my son, as he is always out with his friends or just watching YouTube. So I decided to make a Steam account and get this game to see if I could maybe play alongside him. I loaded into the game, picked my character and started playing but I was stuck on what you where supposed to do. I asked my Son for help and he hosted a game for me to join. I loved it as it was the best time I had spent with my Son since my wife had died. This game has ever since brought me and my son closer again and now we actually spend time together outside the house together as well. This game reminded me that there's fun to be had in everything, and it has brought both me and my Son many happy memories.

author: {'steamid': '76561198013027602', 'num_games_owned': 292, 'num_reviews': 37, 'playtime_forever': 1873, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 1861, 'last_played': 1694824664}
review:
[h1]Do the funky pillar dance![/h1]

Clone Drone in The Danger Zone is a pretty solid game where you play as [b]John Drone[/b]*, a human who has since been turned into a robot for gladiatorial entertainment by other, morally impaired robots.  Your goal is simple; Survive the arena's dangers, and maybe overthrow an evil robotic emperor while you're at it.  Or just that first one.  The plot's lightweight, and outright nonexistent in some areas, and with a game like this, it's relatively okay.  There is a Story Mode that tells a tale of resistance, and the story, while light-weight and offering a simple series of justifications for the enemy gauntlets it hurls you into, also does a great job of introducing new mechanics and weaponry in a rather natural way.
[spoiler]*Clone's name may not be John Drone[/spoiler]

Graphically, this game uses volumetric pixels, or voxels if you're not an [b]utter snob who uses fancy words.[/b]  This means 'Minecraft looks' for those who need further help, and it lends the game a blocky look that only needed a few particle effects to truly shine among the competition in that space.  Obviously, it's very readable at a glance, and with how the game plays, that's important.

Gameplay is semi-simple.  You can wield up to four weapons, a sword, a hammer, a bow, and a spear with shield.  Your goal?  Kill everything else without dying in the process.  Combat controls are simple; Swords and hammers swing where you're moving, or default to a vertical swing if you're still; Bows shoot where you're aiming, spears stab forwards at all times.  You have a dash, a jump, and with upgrades, a kick.  The game's enemies are many, varied, and vast, and all can call for different means of taking them on.  The game balances all it's weapons with strengths and disadvantages, too; While you can go [i]'pew pew'[/i] and kill stuff that way, some robots can deflect arrows.  While your hammer can certainly bonk those guys aside, now you're being shot full of holes by bow-wielding enemies.  While your sword can deflect that, it's range is too short and you are now at risk of receiving the [b]forever bonk[/b] from MC Hammerlots over there.  And while your spear has minced Hammerlots' head, his fifteen friends are now out for your oil.  So on, so forth.  Multiplayer is present and fun, too; Duels, a battle royale that's actually good, and co-operative play all round off an otherwise solid experience, and it's arguably the best part of CDiTDZ.

In terms of performance, this game runs smoothly, but be aware that voxels are anything but lightweight; This game can be a bit taxing on CPUs and GPUs alike in terms of temperature, so make sure your stuff's relatively flame-resistant before going in.  Otherwise, my CPU held a perfectly stable frame rate, save for multiplayer, where server lag becomes everybody's worst enemy, alongside the raptors that fires lasers from their faces.

While the game's story mode is relatively short, a surprisingly addicting Endless mode, several single and multiplayer challenges, and the multiplayer itself make Clone Drone rather replayable, and it supports Workshop levels in case you get tired of the game's stock levels and want to mix things up, from simply adding new arena layouts, to outright adventure maps that go beyond the arena's bounds to create long gauntlets of foes for you to die horribly to.

All told, it's a solid indie package that offers a fun time, and while it's no GoTY contender, Clone Drone is a deliciously delightful time that I can solidly recommend.  [u]Get it at MSRP, you won't be disappointed.[/u]

author: {'steamid': '76561198370149996', 'num_games_owned': 36, 'num_reviews': 11, 'playtime_forever': 5510, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 3099, 'last_played': 1685983597}
review:
This is a game that falls in the "Hard Fun" range of difficulty. My only complaint is the lack of weapons (as of writing this). I would like to see a few new upgrades.
1: Make the great-sword an upgrade instead of restricting it to multiplayer and the level editor.
2: Give the spear a shield re-enforcement upgrade (make it more durable), or give it a range upgrade (make it longer).
3: Give the hammer a faster swing speed or shorter cool-down.
4: Give the bow more arrow width, or more arrow speed.
5: Give the potential for 5 energy bars.
6: Give an even faster get-up upgrade.

For weapons I would like to see.
1: A grenade projectile that has the same effect as spider-tron's bombs. (Range and blast force for upgrades)
2: Dual-wield daggers (a faster but weaker version of sword) (only 2 ticks of projectile block and one tick of fire).
3: Scythe (fire and size upgrades)
4: An actual F***ing Gun (this would use up energy, because it would shoot small energy orbs, and would be deflected by projectile block) (Faster firing speed and less energy consumption for upgrades).
5: Claws like the zombies have (size and fire upgrades).
6: Energy Boomerang (size and fire for upgrades).

MEME weapons.
1: Frying pan (size upgrades).

Weapon re-skins
1: hammer: Stop sign (with an option for an "!" instead of "stop" in reference to "Madness Combat").
2: sword: Katana.
3: spear: Tribal Spear (shield would have a different design on it to).
4: bow: Mechanical Bow.
5: ALL: Choose what color you want the weapons/glow to be (from the already available options).

That is all from me.

author: {'steamid': '76561198894585267', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 5, 'playtime_forever': 4831, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 3319, 'last_played': 1708720153}
review:
This game is a good game. The ability to play in gladiatorial combat without bloodshed makes this game a good choice for children. The multiplayer emotes are earned through actual effort instead of loot crates, and keep the game clean. (No profanity) The story mode has an interesting plot,[spoiler] and the fake human cracks me up every time! [/spoiler]. The achievements are full of diversity and some you may just get accidentally. There is a lot of workshop content existing of: 
Endless Levels
Adventure Levels
And Last bot Standing Levels
The presence of a fun and easy to use level editor always gives me joy, and the ability to toggle between only workshop levels, both workshop levels and regular endless levels, and only regular endless levels is a good feature of the game too. I do feel like the game needs the ability to make custom private duel maps as it is possible to make custom last-bot-standing maps so it would be possible, and it would complete the trifecta of endless, last-bot-standing, and private duels.
Altogether I feel like Clone Drone In the Danger Zone is a good game.

author: {'steamid': '76561199201190751', 'num_games_owned': 56, 'num_reviews': 2, 'playtime_forever': 3694, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 1912, 'last_played': 1690812232}
review: 很好的游戏，完美的打击感，各种隐藏成就和彩蛋，剧情模式丰富而不冗杂，其他模式也很赞！2017年玩的盗版，后来注入steam毫不犹豫买下了它，可以说，它是我心目中最棒的游戏！十分推荐！（长矛其实很好玩，在攻击那段时间矛头对于所有方向都有攻击性，你甚至可以通过旋转一周来达到剑拦腰砍断的效果，就是他妈随机升级太操蛋了，巨难，但我已经解锁了全挑战成就）

Um jogo com uma dificuldade muito elevada, e em certos momentos chega a ser injusto, lhe colocando contra vários oponentes poderosos de uma só vez. Porém, no geral, consegue ser bem divertido, e a satisfação ao zerar o modo história é imensa, uma ótima jogatina para passar o tempo, mas recomendo comprar durante uma promoção.
Nota: 7/10

author: {'steamid': '76561198860416238', 'num_games_owned': 124, 'num_reviews': 8, 'playtime_forever': 1001, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 957, 'last_played': 1660409292}
review:
[h1] Clone Drone in the Danger Zone [/h1]

[i] Voxel-Destruction türünün en iyi örneklerinden olan  "Clone Drone in the Danger Zone" aynı zamanda başarılı bir beat-em-up oyunu . Kılıcınızla vurduğunuz her darbenin verdiği hasarı anlık olarak görebileceğiniz , minik ama tatlı hikayesi ile sizi bir kaç saatliğine gerçek dünyadan soyutlayacak harika bir oyun [/i]

[b] Lore [/b]
[i] Farklı evrenlerden gelen üstün zekalı robotlar bütün Samanyolu galaksisini işgal etmiş durumdadır . İnsanların kendini savunacak gücü yoktur , robotlar bunu fırsat bilip geride sadece dünya kalacak şekilde tüm gezegenleri ele geçirmiştir . Dünyanın ve tabii ki de insanlığın sonu neredeyse kaçınılmaz olmuştur . Ancak bir kadın tüm insanlığın kaderini değiştirecek bir şey yapmıştır , kendi gezegeni robotların istilası altındayken  zihnini robotların iletişim ağına yükleyip yıllarca bir bilgisayar virüsü gibi orada yaşamış , kehanetin gerçekleşeceği gün ise insanlığın son umudu olmuştur [/i]

[b] Hikaye [/b]
[i] İnsan vücudu başka yaşam formlarına karşı çok dayanıksız olduğu için onları bu şekilde kullanmak pek yararlı olmayacaktır . Robotlar kaçırdıkları insanların zihinlerini bir robot vücuduna aktarıp onları arenalarda güçlü robotlarını test etmek için denek olarak kullanıyordur . Çoğu insan her ne kadar robot vücudunda olsa dahi en fazla 1 , 2 bölüm sonra dayanamayıp ölüyor dur . Biz ise bu arenaya düşen herhangi birini oynuyoruz çünkü her öldüğümüzde yerimize yeni bir insan geçiyor ve onun gözünden oynamaya devam ediyoruz . Stage 10'a geçtiğimiz vakit gizemli bir kadın hologramı bizimle iletişime geçiyor ve az önceki bölümden kalma robot kalıntılarını toplayan "Garbage Bot"ların geleceği yerin kapağını bizim için acacağını tüm insanlığın kaderinin bizim ellerimizde olduğunu söylüyor . Delikten geçtikten sonra Robotlar çıldırıyor ve bizi durdurmaya çalışıyor ancak çıkış kapısının önünden geçen bir arabaya atlayıp oradan uzaklaştığımızda bizi bulamayacakları bir yere gidiyoruz . Tahmin edebileceğiniz üzere o kadın hologramı az önce anlattığım kadınla aynı kişi . Adının "Emilia" olduğunu belirten ablamız robotların liderleri olan yüce "Emperor" un dünyaya yapacağı istilanın yakında olduğunu söylüyor ve zaten yarı insan yarı robot olan zihnimizi dünyaya saldırması muhtemel olan bir geminin filosunda ki rastgele bir askere yükleyeceğini o asker ile farkedilmeden gemiyi ele geçirip istilayı durdurmamızı istiyor . Hikayemiz ana amaç olarak bu konuyu esas alıyor .

[b] Oynanış [/b]
[i] Evet oyunun asıl olayı olan oynanış kısmına geldik , en başta da söylediğim üzere bu oyun bir voxel-destruction oyunu . Kısaca pixel parçalanma oyunu . Oyunun ilk chapterlarında arena da olduğumuz için basit Sword-Robot ve Archer-Bot lar ile karşılaşıyoruz . Tabi bu böyle basit gitmiyor biz bölüm geçtiğimiz zaman her robot güncelleme alıyor . Örneğin "Archer-Bot Mark 1" basit ve pek akıllı olmayan bir okçu iken Mark 2 sürümünde daha hızlı ok atabilmenin yanında sizi beklemediğiniz anda yakalamaya çalışıyor . Mark 4 gibi üst seviyelere geldiğimizde yay ve ok kullanmanın yanında alevli kılıçlar vesaire de kullanabilir hale geliyorlar [/i] 

[i] Standart düşman tipi olarak görebileceğimiz 5 Robot çeşidi var ekstraları saymaz isek . Bunlar : Sword-Robot , Archer-Bot , Spider-Tron , Hammer-Bot ve Jetpack-Botlar dır . Her biri bölüm ilerledikçe ortaya çıkmaya ve sürüm atladıkça yeni özellikler kazanıp güçlenmeye devam ediyor . Tabi onlar güçleniyorsa biz neden güçlenmeyelim ? Her bölümden sonra asansöre binip alt kattaki upgrade bot un yanına gidiyoruz ve bölümden gelen 1 puanımızla karakterimizi güçlendirebiliyoruz . Oyuna en çeşitlilik sağlayan unsurlardan biri bu güncelleme kısmı . Her oynanışınızda yeni bir build yapabilirsiniz . Bir "Sword Master" veya bir 300 Spartalı edası ile Mızrak , Kalkan ikilisi yapabilirsiniz . Jetpack , Yanan Oklar , Ateş Üfleme , Spartan Tekmesi... ve daha bir sürü şeyi robotunuza takıp güçlü buildler ile tekrar tekrar bitirebilirsiniz oyunu . [/i]

[i] Attığınız bir darbenin düşmanınızı öldürmeyip onu sakat bıraktığına bile şahit olabilirsiniz , küçük dünyasında dolu dolu bir deneyim sunuyor bütün bunların üstüne daily challengelar , co-op modu , multiplayer arena gibi modları ve updateler ile oyunu devamlı oynanabilir ve güncel tutuyorlar . İndirimde kaçırmayın derim [/i]

Puan : 7.4

author: {'steamid': '76561198291023551', 'num_games_owned': 0, 'num_reviews': 4, 'playtime_forever': 3415, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 182, 'playtime_at_review': 1379, 'last_played': 1711781079}
review: Clone Drone in the Danger Zone is a simple game, you simply fight robots and kill robots while trying not to die in the danger zone. From the outside your first look might be "this game looks really simple and the style reminds me of Minecraft with the "blockyness", but let me tell you there is so much more to this game than it seems. The story: The story was one of the things that got me and my brother hooked to this game, the story seems so simple and the next thing you know, your in a completely different feeling game. The physics: The physics are pretty good when it comes to aiming your weapon, you see your able to cut off different limbs depending on where your looking while your swing, and if you take damage you don't die right away (sometimes) instead you can still fight while only having... lets say half of your boy, one arm, 2 knees, half a head gone, its pretty astounding really. Online mode and Extras: once your done with the base game there are still a lot of things you can do like for example fight together or against other players. The game gives your challenges in order to unlock trophies, upgrades, or skins if your playing online. There's also an endless mode where you have to keep fighting and see how far you can go. This game seems so simple and it... kinda is, but if you can find the true beauty of this game, you will love it.

author: {'steamid': '76561198939497930', 'num_games_owned': 107, 'num_reviews': 21, 'playtime_forever': 24605, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 11590, 'last_played': 1707311309}
review:
很不错的游戏，不过没以前那么火了。现在好像有点"凉""了。。。但真的是一款好游戏！打击感真的特别爽！我记得当初是看鲤鱼Ace的视频入了坑，我以前背着父母偷偷买被发现了，被痛打了一顿，然后退了款，但现在我成绩进步了，又重新入了坑，这游戏画质建模真的比以前好太多了！游戏可玩性还是很大的，除了玩故事模式和原有的关卡和挑战外还可以和别人玩多人模式！这些玩腻了还可以去创意工坊找些冒险挑战无尽关卡来玩！你可以去创意工坊搜【CannonShockMaster's levels】这是合集，里面有我做的无尽模式关卡，都是我比较成功的作品！ 但我还是想说几句，官方能不能限制一下创意工坊发布关卡数目！我是一个无尽关卡的作者吧，我用心花了三四天乃至几周做的关卡，刚发布不到一天，最新关卡那栏我昨天还在第一第二位，第二天居然经常可以排到倒数几列了，排前的都是一
堆黄金战神国王啊，几个乱摆点东西的啊，我真的很烦！我辛辛苦苦做了那么久，你倒好,打几个【不可能】【你能过得去吗】【国王】【非常难】的词汇，一天发好几个都不带累的!关卡搞得那么难,又没几个人想订阅，做出来有什么意思! 我觉得官方可以限制用户一天24小时内只能发一个关卡，不然一大堆垃圾摆在那把好的东西掩埋了有什么意义？我是CannonShockMaster！如果你看到这篇评论觉得我是个自私的人，欢迎你来怼我！你可以随便说我的关卡是垃圾！随便说！反正我之前上过热门前列。。。。呵呵，我无法在讨论区留言，所以我要看看有多少个人会怼我。嘿嘿

author: {'steamid': '76561198413582663', 'num_games_owned': 47, 'num_reviews': 4, 'playtime_forever': 1744, 'playtime_last_two_weeks': 0, 'playtime_at_review': 1414, 'last_played': 1686334082}
review:
Это  первый мой осознанный обзор на игру в стиме. Не будьте строги.
1.Вступление.
Игру я купил когда она была популярна на YouTube. Сначала она казалась мне сложной, но позже я понял, что это не так. Я прошел большинство испытаний( режим ,который ты проходишь только одним оружием или навыком). Играл в бесконечном режиме. Прошел сюжетку. Это мой второй акк. Но наиграл 54 часа. Пробовал пару кастомок. Этим хочу сказать, что в игре легко разобраться.
2. Геймплей. 
Главное, чем цепляет игра(для меня)  это задумка. Разрушаемость врагов и твоего бота в том числе. Редактор, в которых ты можешь сделать кастомку (арену, паркур, тропу, даже свою карту с сюжетом). Боёвка в этой игре сначала увлекает,  но позже становится скучно. Однообразная арена, враги, цель.            
Ботов очень много, но большинство из них объединяется в группы по оружию и проходится по тактике.
Оружия тоже не мало. Однако есть меты. Я обожаю классический меч, но так и не понимаю "прикол" копья.
В итоге все выше перечисленное тупо надоест. Играть станет скучно.
3. Мультиплеер.
В игре два мультиплеер режима. Первый-дуэль. Второй -королевская битва. О ней много не скажешь. Королевская битва сделана неплохо. Прикольный выбор перса( если это можно так назвать). Карты( но скорее большие арены, тоже сделаны неплохо). НО что связывает эти режимы онлайн части игры, это их сырость. Ты будешь попадаться с в прямом смысле "ботами", челами, которые живут этой игрой. Многие говорят, что есть читеры. Возможно, так и есть. Ведь античита в игре вроде как и нет. По поводу баланса есть поправка( маленький онлайн) , потому я не беру это за недочет. И в конце скажу у меня в онлайне лаги.
4. Графика и окружение. 
О графике глупо что-то говорить ведь игра из разряда кубическая инди-арена. Но вот окружение реально слишком квадратное и не детализированное. Уровни сделаны из кубов, ровных плит и тд. Можно сделать какой-то декор, добавить на стены выпуклостей, вогнутостей.
5. О сюжете ничего особого не скажешь.
6. Мои предложения к игре.
 Мне кажется, что можно сделать разнообразные ачивки, добавить декор на уровни. Наделать ещё разных режимов пве. 
7. Мне игра нравится. Она может увлечь. Но и может быстро надоесть. Её минусы можно списать на малое количество разработчиков.
